			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Simbiose da Administração com a Tecnologia</strong> (2021) — UESPI. Relationship between
				technology and administration.
			</li>
		</ul>

		<hr class='my-8 border-blue-100' />

		<h2 class='text-2xl font-medium text-blue-800 mt-8'>Blog posts</h2>
		<p class='text-blue-800'>Selected articles I've published:</p>
		<ul class='text-blue-800 space-y-2'>
			<li>
				<a
					href='https://dev.to/candidosales/migrate-strapi-from-render-to-flyio-lbi'
